---
title: HEPAQ — Secuencia · Registrar Diagnóstico (con CIE-10 y Cache Decorator)
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Medico as Médico
    participant APIM as Azure API Management
    participant Controller as DiagnosticosController
    participant Delegate as DiagnosticoDelegate
    participant UseCase as RegistrarDiagnosticoUseCase
    participant CieAdp as CieTableAdapter
    participant TableStorage as Azure Table Storage
    participant Decorator as DiagnosticoCacheDecorator
    participant RedisAdp as DiagnosticoRedisAdapter
    participant RedisDB as Azure Cache for Redis
    participant JpaAdp as DiagnosticoJpaAdapter
    participant SQL as Azure SQL Database
    participant CosmosAdp as DiagnosticoCosmosAdapter
    participant CosmosDB as Azure Cosmos DB
    participant SBPub as ServiceBusPublisher
    participant SB as Azure Service Bus

    Medico->>APIM: POST /diagnosticos/v1/diagnosticos [Bearer JWT]
    APIM->>APIM: Validar JWT + verificar rol MEDICO
    APIM->>Controller: registrarDiagnostico(RegistrarDiagnosticoRequest)
    Controller->>Delegate: registrarDiagnostico(request)
    Delegate->>UseCase: ejecutar(RegistrarDiagnosticoCmd)

    Note over UseCase,TableStorage: Validación del código CIE-10

    UseCase->>CieAdp: obtenerPorCodigo(codigoCIE)
    CieAdp->>TableStorage: GET /cie10/{codigo}
    TableStorage-->>CieAdp: CodigoCIE {codigo, descripcion, categoria}
    CieAdp-->>UseCase: CodigoCIE válido

    Note over UseCase,Decorator: Decorator Pattern — Cache transparente

    UseCase->>Decorator: guardar(diagnostico)
    Decorator->>JpaAdp: guardar(diagnostico)
    JpaAdp->>SQL: INSERT INTO diagnosticos (...) VALUES (...)
    SQL-->>JpaAdp: OK · id generado
    JpaAdp-->>Decorator: Diagnostico persistido
    Decorator->>RedisAdp: put(diagnosticoId, diagnostico)
    RedisAdp->>RedisDB: SET diag:{id} TTL=600s
    RedisDB-->>RedisAdp: OK
    Decorator-->>UseCase: Diagnostico guardado

    Note over UseCase,CosmosDB: Sincronización Read Model (CQRS)

    UseCase->>CosmosAdp: guardar(diagnosticoDocument)
    CosmosAdp->>CosmosDB: upsert /diagnosticos/{id}
    CosmosDB-->>CosmosAdp: OK

    Note over UseCase,SB: Publicación de Evento de Dominio

    UseCase->>SBPub: publish(DiagnosticoRegistradoEvent)
    SBPub->>SB: Message → topic: diagnosticos-registrados
    SB-->>SBPub: ACK

    UseCase-->>Delegate: DiagnosticoDTO
    Delegate-->>Controller: DiagnosticoDTO
    Controller-->>APIM: 201 Created
    APIM-->>Medico: 201 Created {diagnosticoId, codigoCIE, estado: ACTIVO}

    Note over Medico,RedisDB: Lectura posterior con cache (Decorator)

    Medico->>APIM: GET /diagnosticos/v1/diagnosticos/{id}
    APIM->>Controller: obtenerDiagnostico(id)
    Controller->>Delegate: obtenerDiagnostico(id)
    Delegate->>UseCase: obtener(id)
    UseCase->>Decorator: obtener(id)
    Decorator->>RedisAdp: get(diagnosticoId)
    RedisAdp->>RedisDB: GET diag:{id}
    alt Cache hit
        RedisDB-->>RedisAdp: DiagnosticoEntity (serializado)
        RedisAdp-->>Decorator: DiagnosticoEntity
        Decorator-->>UseCase: Diagnostico (sin tocar SQL)
    else Cache miss
        RedisDB-->>RedisAdp: nil
        Decorator->>JpaAdp: obtener(id)
        JpaAdp->>SQL: SELECT * FROM diagnosticos WHERE id = ?
        SQL-->>JpaAdp: DiagnosticoEntity
        JpaAdp-->>Decorator: DiagnosticoEntity
        Decorator->>RedisAdp: put(id, entity) TTL=600s
        Decorator-->>UseCase: Diagnostico
    end
    UseCase-->>Delegate: DiagnosticoDTO
    Controller-->>APIM: 200 OK
    APIM-->>Medico: 200 OK DiagnosticoDTO
